  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the tava or griddle to medium-high heat.",
    "Soak wooden skewers in water for at least 30 minutes before use.",
    "Thread chicken breast onto skewers, leaving a small space between each piece.",
    "Brush coconut oil on the tava or griddle to prevent sticking.",
    "Grill chicken for 8-10 minutes per side, or until cooked through.",
    "Meanwhile, mix miso paste, honey, rice vinegar, grated ginger, and black pepper in a small bowl until smooth.",
    "Once chicken is cooked, brush miso glaze on each piece.",
    "Sprinkle Colby Jack cheese, green onions, and sesame seeds on top of the chicken.",
    "Cook for an additional 1-2 minutes, or until cheese is melted.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy!"
  ],
